  "detailed_description": "<h1>Update Notes</h1><p>The game now has a difficulty setting, go try it out.</p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>Flippen Run Mike is a  2d, cartoony, platforming game where running and hiding are the only options you have.<br><br>Every enemy is a \"Boss\" and can end your attempt to keep Mike alive in one hit. <br><br><strong>This game is designed to be difficult and is going to challenge you over and over through trial and error.</strong><br><br>You need to try and complete the 40 unique levels in eight realms.<br><br>Find the \"hidden\" character in four different stages (pro tip - do not miss one encounter).<br><br>There is no in-game map stages are maze-like. Also, who has a map of the sewers?<br><br>Unique storyline.<br><br>This game might be offensive to some players the content in this game is satire.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1460910/extras/1081ef1c48edf1056f75d8b7d97b0440.poster.avif?t=1606998251\" width=506 height=506 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1460910/extras/1081ef1c48edf1056f75d8b7d97b0440.webm?t=1606998251\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1460910/extras/1081ef1c48edf1056f75d8b7d97b0440.mp4?t=1606998251\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
